info:
岗位职责:
1、定期对私募基金产品周报、月度宣传材料进行更新;
2、完成资方尽调报告材料填写制作;
3、协助支持市场前台销售工作，包括合格投资者认证、数据更新、净值设置发送等;
4、负责市场部各类会议的组织与跟进;
任职要求:
1、一流院校毕业生/大四在校实习生
2、具备出色的沟通能力，能够高效地与团队成员和客户进行互动;
3、能够在规定时间内完成上级交付的任务，并保持工作质量;
4、服务意识强，且具有良好的团队合作精神，能够迅速适应团队环境，共同推进项目。
必备条件（请严格对照，非诚勿扰）：
1.较为全面的了解私募证券投资基金基础知识及运作流程，有私募证券投资基金从业资格的优先；
2.具备较强的学习能力和逻辑判断能力；
3.具备熟练的文字处理、图表处理、数据分析处理能力；
4.工作态度认真、细致，追求材料格式和内容的完整性和完美度（具有强迫属性）；
5.有金融行业的从业规划或发展愿景。
彩蛋：对实习期表现特别优秀的或有突出市场贡献的，公司提供额外奖金鼓励，并对有长远从业意愿的保持长期实习合作，提供职业规划建议，保留正式职业岗位。

JD for the intern:

•Support the routine contract management process, including contract filing, data quality check in contract management system, original contract receipt status tracking, etc.;

•Support contract management system upgrade if necessary, e.g. user acceptance test, training material preparation;

•Support the user change management for APAC region, e.g. monitor the user status change, follow-up with status of contracts transfer;

•Prepare contract analysis report where necessary;

•Ad hoc tasks from LIPC

Requirements:

•大三或大四

•没有专业限制

•英文流利，至少邮件沟通没问题

•有责任心，认真仔细

•需要不定期去漕泾

JD
Transportation Part:

Check the accuracy of invoice report between the whole Asia plants(9 countries and 25 plants) and 7 world level forwarders via our advanced system by monthly basis;
Analyse the shipment data and figure out the optimization for our status, for instance, dig out the space utilization or try to explore an alternative transportation model;
Forwarder(Suppliers) Management Part:

Estimate forwarders’ performance through our internal standard. During this period, you have the opportunity to reform and improve the criteria of forwarder selection & evaluation;
Prepare and participate into the quarterly business meeting with forwarders;
Others:

Have enormous challenging projects and you are not just focus on transportation, you will act as the back up to support another function like warehouse & packaging more than packaging data upload, which means you are able to confront the most comprehensive dimension of supply chain;
Some activities support, like workshop, dept meeting preparation, etc.;

Job Requirement:

Excellent English skills;
Prefer candidates whose major is in supply chain, industry engineering, logistics, economics, etc.;
Photography and video recording skills is a plus;
More than 3 days/W,  6 months at least ;
